Drive commercial negotiations with publishers, platforms, and ad-tech partners to ensure cost competitiveness and value optimization.
Collaborate with digital planning, client leadership, and performance teams to execute integrated and efficient media strategies.
Deliver on investment KPIs, audit readiness, and rate adherence in alignment with WPP Media’s trading and compliance standards.
Oversee budget management, delivery tracking, and post-buy analysis for key campaigns.
Partner with WPP Media trading and digital excellence teams to identify innovations, first-mover opportunities, and beta partnerships.
Lead a team of digital buyers and executives, ensuring strong capability building and operational discipline.
Provide market intelligence, platform insights, and cost benchmarks to support new business pitches and client strategy discussions.
Ensure adherence to WPP Media governance frameworks and compliance across all digital investment operations. 
Strong understanding of digital media platforms, programmatic ecosystems, and biddable buying.
Proven ability to negotiate, optimize, and deliver cost efficiencies while maintaining quality and performance.
Hands-on experience with DV360, CM360, Google Ads, Meta Ads Manager, and analytics tools.
Strong analytical and quantitative skills; comfort with data interpretation and reporting.
Excellent stakeholder management skills with the ability to work cross-functionally.
Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, matrixed organization and manage multiple client priorities.

