9
• Own the Number: You will be the single owner of our primary growth KPIs: Net User Growth, Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC), and Lifetime Value (LTV).
• Architect the Engine: You will design, build, and lead a multi-disciplinary growth organization spanning Performance Marketing, SEO, Content, Community, Referrals, and Lifecycle/CRM.
• Master the Flywheel: You will develop a deep, quantitative understanding of our powerful organic loop and build strategies to accelerate it. You will not just spend a budget; you will invest capital into the channels with the highest, most sustainable returns.
• Scale New Channels: You will take our early success in paid channels (Meta/Google) and build a sophisticated, scalable performance marketing function. You will also experiment with and unlock new, unconventional channels.
• Drive Product-Led Growth: You will work directly with the CEO and the product/engineering teams to identify and execute on growth opportunities within the product itself. You will be the voice of the user, constantly looking for ways to improve activation, retention, and referral rates.
• Build a Data-Driven Culture: You will be the champion of data within the company. You will implement the systems, tools, and processes required to ensure every growth decision is backed by rigorous analysis and experimentation.
