• Identify, prioritize and optimize customer acquisition and retention channels.
• Collaborate cross-functionally with Product, Analytics and Business teams to capitalize on growth opportunities and increase client satisfaction through cohesive strategies
• Own the growth marketing budget- Optimize ROI across campaigns and initiatives
• Drive growth of platforms leveraging content and SEO marketing and drive the brand, content and SEO strategy
Customer Acquisition and Activation
• Drive digital acquisition, activation, retention and monitor competition.
• Lead Performance marketing efforts across paid, organic and referral channels (eg Google Ads, Meta, LinkedIn, SEO, GEO, ASO and Affiliates)
• Develop segmented acquisition campaigns for different customer personas to create and maintain high levels of customer interaction
• Oversee social media accounts, manage and improve online content, considering SEO and Google Analytics
• Optimize lead scoring, CRM workflows and automation systems for conversion efficiency.
• Manage end to end funnel of conversion in collaboration with inside sales team of the Bank where required
Retention and Engagement
• Analyse user behaviour (heat map / click stream data / drop off data) and key business problems to identify opportunities
• Design and execute personalized lifecycle programs (email, push notifications, in-app communication) to increase engagement.
• Define and manage key business events for campaign targeting and retargeting.
• Track campaign wise conversions across segments & campaigns modes (campaign analysis, AB testing, funnel optimization)
• Develop loyalty and referral programs
